INTRODUCTION:
      In the pursuit of simplicity and
efficiency in lighting solutions, this project introduces an auto light system 
employing a straightforward approach with ultrasonictecnology, by harnessing
the basics of ultrasonic sensors,the systems aims to create an uncomplicated
yet effective method for automatic lighting control.this report provides an 
overview of the fundamental concept and application of the proposed auto
light system,highlighting its potential for ease of implementattion and
user-friendly operation 
